title: News Roundup & Top 25 Free Agents
itunes:title: News Roundup & Top 25 Free Agents
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the league including Jason Garrett heading to the Giants (12:35), Titans DC Dean Pees retiring after 16 seasons (14:57) and some potential rule changes for the league. (29:33). The heroes debate Gregg's list of top 25 free agents including some big names like Tom Brady, Drew Brees and Derrick Henry. (39:53)
